      • getParent

        public E getParent(E object)
        Public method to get the parent of an element that has been found in the search. Return null if it is the root. If the object has not been yet found, this method will return null too. ¡Be careful!
        Parameters:
        object - Object to check
        Returns:
        E with the parent of object. If it is the root of the search, returns null.
